source.name: NOLA Street Centerlines
source.description: City of New Orleans street centerlines.  ESRI shapefile format, GIS software required for viewing geometry (http://www.esri.com/software/arcgis/arcreader/).  Tabular data (DBF), included as part of the shapefile, are viewable in Excel.  Scheduled update: weekly
